        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          The Atomic Update
          (<link
          xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=905330"/>).
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          Upgrading to SLE 12
          (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=904188"/>).
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          Intermediate step: Updating SLE 11 SP2 to SLE 11 SP3
          (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=904186"/>).
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          Supported Upgrade Paths to SLE
          (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=904182"/>).
